  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The simulation is intended for use in pre-market submission support for a Class II spinal fixation device, evaluated against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors are assessed; the Test conditions factor is rated below required level due to a single test condition being exercised. Decision: Accepted at Medium assurance level.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-f1717-noncannulated-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-fea-ensemble-pedicle-screw-v1",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-experimental-n11-lab1",
